A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Atlanta News First (Atlanta WANF-TV) for its outstanding
2 contribution to civic engagement and patriotism through the "Pledge of the Day" initiative;
3 and for other purposes.
4 WHEREAS, Atlanta News First (WANF-TV) has demonstrated an unwavering commitment
5 to fostering patriotism and civic responsibility among the youth of Georgia through the
6 "Pledge of the Day" initiative; and
7 WHEREAS, under the leadership of Erik Schrader, President and General Manager of
8 Atlanta News First (WANF-TV), Atlanta News First has provided a platform for elementary
9 school students across metro Atlanta to lead the Pledge of Allegiance, instilling in them a
10 sense of national pride and unity; and
11 WHEREAS, this initiative was developed in 2024 by Representative Kim Schofield of House
12 District 63, Atlanta, with the vision of expanding its reach to engage elementary schools
13 across the State of Georgia; and
